_:N6b191a2b02f44c61a8fcdc5ecc2b5fcf <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Anneliese Dodds was Minister for Development at the Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office and Minister for Women and Equalities at the Department for Education from 8 July 2024 until 28 February 2025. She was elected as the MP for Oxford East in June 2017.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n  <p>Follow Anneliese on X/Twitter:  <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://x.com/AnnelieseDodds\">@AnnelieseDodds</a></p>\n</div>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
